Oh, you don't think
she's still alive.

785
01:02:49,920 --> 01:02:52,640
If a kid could see her
in a coma, then why...

786
01:02:52,720 --> 01:02:55,080
couldn't she be trying to
communicate from one?

787
01:02:55,160 --> 01:02:59,840
