government searched the jungle for a month.

788
01:02:59,920 --> 01:03:02,840
And never found her! Exactly.
And that's why we're here tonight-

789
01:03:02,880 --> 01:03:06,080
because you never saw her body
and never got closure.

790
01:03:09,720 --> 01:03:11,560
Emily's dead, Joe.

791
01:03:12,760 --> 01:03:14,600
That's what
this is all about-

792
01:03:14,680 --> 01:03:16,600
your refusal
to accept that.

793
