You have to
end this, Joe.

797
01:03:30,720 --> 01:03:34,040
You gotta do the hard stuff, like I did.

798
01:03:34,120 --> 01:03:36,120
Like everyone does.

799
01:03:36,160 --> 01:03:39,200
You gotta clean out the
closets, empty the drawers...

800
01:03:39,280 --> 01:03:43,800
