What do you mean,
what about it?

805
01:04:07,200 --> 01:04:10,080
Well, anything to get
your mind off of this.

806
01:04:10,120 --> 01:04:12,000
So, you think
I should go?

807
01:04:12,040 --> 01:04:14,400
Maybe I'll go
with you. Huh?

808
01:04:14,440 --> 01:04:17,040
I'm mean with a paddle.

809
