I want us all to go home,
go over our river maps.

812
01:04:26,320 --> 01:04:29,240
Note the hazard points,
the portages, the waterfalls.

813
01:04:29,280 --> 01:04:31,840
Oh, check out these safari
pants. It says to pack light.

814
