No, I mean- I mean,
do you think it'll sell?

821
01:05:08,720 --> 01:05:10,640
The agent said
it needed a paint job.

822
01:05:10,680 --> 01:05:13,240
Oh, get what you can
and get out.

823
01:05:13,280 --> 01:05:16,720
Leave the memories behind.
You didn't after Hannah died.

824
01:05:16,800 --> 01:05:20,280
Yeah, but I didn't have corpses
playing ventriloquist with me either.

825
01:05:22,480 --> 01:05:25,680
I'm gonna miss you, Joe.

