01:05:25,760 --> 01:05:27,600
I'm gonna
miss your waffles.

827
01:05:30,920 --> 01:05:34,320
Would you show it for me
if I'm gone for a week?

828
01:05:34,400 --> 01:05:38,280
- I'm taking that white-water trip.
- With pleasure.

829
01:05:38,360 --> 01:05:40,680
It's good to see you
joining the world again.

830
01:10:05,640 --> 01:10:08,280
Hello. Hal. Reading
the map of the river...

831
01:10:08,320 --> 01:10:11,920
there's a symbol
- two wavery lines that crisscross in the middle.

832
01:10:12,000 --> 01:10:15,960
Waterfalls. Put a big red circle around
those. We'll have to portage there.

833
01:10:16,040 --> 01:10:17,920
They're too high
this time of year.

834
01:10:20,160 --> 01:10:22,040
Joe?

835
01:10:52,440 --> 01:10:54,960
A rainbow.

836
01:11:16,520 --> 01:11:18,520
You are, uh, the doctor? Yes.

837
01:11:18,560 --> 01:11:20,560
Muy bien.

838
01:11:24,760 --> 01:11:28,200
Is my pilot here?
That is me. Eh, Victor.

839
01:11:29,360 --> 01:11:31,480
¿Cómo te vas?

