01:11:35,360 --> 01:11:37,840
Don't worry.
I know how.

842
01:11:37,920 --> 01:11:40,480
You have a license, though, right? ;Sí.

843
01:11:40,560 --> 01:11:42,440
Pretty much.

844
01:11:47,680 --> 01:11:49,600
Juanajuapa.

845
01:11:49,680 --> 01:11:51,520
Juanajuapa,
you've been there?

846
01:11:51,600 --> 01:11:53,400
Sí, Juanajuapa.

847
01:11:54,480 --> 01:11:57,240
This is it, right?

848
01:11:58,240 --> 01:12:00,200
With the waterfall?

