through me.

853
01:12:15,920 --> 01:12:18,240
Okay, we go.

854
01:12:28,600 --> 01:12:32,800
Is that your girlfriend?
In the picture?

855
01:12:32,840 --> 01:12:35,240
It's my wife.

856
01:12:35,320 --> 01:12:37,240
Used to be.

857
01:12:38,680 --> 01:12:41,760
You come
to get her back, eh?

858
