any worse,
we don't get outta here.

886
01:17:54,080 --> 01:17:55,960
And- And that's
no good for nobody.

887
01:18:21,680 --> 01:18:24,120
Señors.

888
01:18:24,200 --> 01:18:26,080
Señors, uh...

889
01:18:26,120 --> 01:18:28,760
my wife.
Su esposa.

890
01:18:28,840 --> 01:18:31,600
Mi esposa.
Red Cross.

891
01:18:31,680 --> 01:18:34,840
- La Cruz Roja.
- Cruz Roja. Where?

892
01:18:34,880 --> 01:18:36,800
¿Dónde?
¿Dónde?

893
01:18:36,840 --> 01:18:39,400
Does any-
Does anybody know where?

894
01:18:39,480 --> 01:18:42,320
Which one?

895
01:18:47,640 --> 01:18:50,840
- What are they saying?
- They say they know her.

896
01:18:59,640 --> 01:19:03,640
What's he saying now? He says he
wants to take you to the village.

