Joe.

908
01:22:57,320 --> 01:22:59,200
- Join her.
- Joe! - Joe!

909
01:22:59,240 --> 01:23:01,160
Joe, can't you hear me?

910
01:23:02,240 --> 01:23:04,480
Joe?

911
01:23:04,560 --> 01:23:07,680
A hundred steps on the ladder
of consciousness. Go there.

912
01:23:11,040 --> 01:23:12,920
No survivors.
Where's her body?

913
01:23:12,960 --> 01:23:15,200
Think she's still alive.
- Emily!

914
01:23:15,280 --> 01:23:18,440
- Joe?
- Listen to me!

915
01:26:26,840 --> 01:26:28,960
You are one crazy son of
a bitch, you know that?

916
01:26:29,040 --> 01:26:31,400
You are lucky to be alive,
señor. You were not breathing.

917
01:26:31,480 --> 01:26:34,240
