01:29:01,840 --> 01:29:03,680
Mi- Mi esposa.

933
01:29:05,920 --> 01:29:08,520
Did you know her?

934
01:29:12,280 --> 01:29:14,640
Mi esposa.

935
01:29:19,720 --> 01:29:23,320
Doctore.

936
01:29:23,360 --> 01:29:28,760
Doctore. Mi esposa.

937
01:29:31,600 --> 01:29:33,240
Mi esposa.

938
01:29:35,760 --> 01:29:38,120
The waterfall.

939
01:29:38,200 --> 01:29:40,880
She was here.

940
01:30:14,240 --> 01:30:17,760
She say
they knew her alive.

941
01:30:17,840 --> 01:30:19,960
She came to help them...

942
01:30:21,200 --> 01:30:24,560
