brought her back...

943
01:30:25,600 --> 01:30:27,520
dying.

944
01:30:40,200 --> 01:30:43,320
They could not save
her body...

945
01:30:43,360 --> 01:30:46,560
but they save her soul.

946
01:32:40,920 --> 01:32:43,560
She said, "dragonfly. "

