01:33:10,720 --> 01:33:14,160
at least while she was
of mind and body.

949
01:33:14,240 --> 01:33:18,000
And I don't know how the
baby survived- premature-

950
01:33:18,080 --> 01:33:21,120
so small and fragile
in the middle of the jungle.

951
01:33:23,480 --> 01:33:27,720
What I do know is that Emily made sure
our child found her way into my arms.

952
01:33:29,120 --> 01:33:34,040
What she taught me in life,
she taught me in death-

953
01:33:34,080 --> 01:33:37,800
to trust, to have faith.

954
01:33:40,160 --> 01:33:42,480
Because as a friend
of mine once said...

